<Name>DevEnviro.as</Name>
<Status>Partially Operational (30%)</Status>
<Description>The orchestrator project. A critical architectural flaw in the AgentRegistry and a restart loop in the Gemini CLI Listener container remain as active blockers. Its Python environment is now stable.</Description>
</Project>
<Project id="project_ingest_llm">
<Name>InGest-LLM.as</Name>
<Status>Partially Operational (70%)</Status>
<Description>Microservice for data ingestion. A root-cause PYTHONPATH issue preventing container startup has been identified. Its Python environment is now stable.</Description>
</Project>
<Project id="project_memos">
<Name>memOS.as</Name>
<Status>Operational</Status>
<Description>The primary project is 'Operation: memOS Upgrade', a multi-phase plan now beginning with 'Phase 0: Monorepo Integration'. Its Python environment is now stable after resolving structural issues in its source repository.</Description>
</Project>
<Project id="project_tools">
<Name>tools.as</Name>
<Status>Partially Operational (40%)</Status>
<Description>Tool registry microservice. The API service is offline and requires deployment. Its Python environment is now stable.</Description>
</Project>
